OL,4,CSupreme Court to rule on car finance
OL,5,Crow
OL,7,FThe Supreme Court is to rule on Friday
OL,8,Fon whether millions of motorists could
OL,9,Fbe entitled to compensation on their
OL,10,Fhire-purchase agreements.
OL,12,FIn October last year, the Court of
OL,13,FAppeal ruled that "secret" commission
OL,14,Fpayments to car dealers as part of
OL,15,Ffinance arrangements made before 2021
OL,16,Fwithout the motorist's fully informed
OL,17,Fconsent were unlawful.
