OL,5,Crow
OL,7,FThe court found that three motorists,
OL,8,Fwho all bought their cars before 2021,
OL,9,Fhad not been told either clearly
OL,10,Fenough or at all that the car dealers,
OL,11,Facting as credit brokers, would
OL,12,Freceive a commission from the lenders
OL,13,Ffor introducing business to them, and
OL,14,Fshould receive compensation.
OL,16,FTwo lenders, FirstRand Bank and Close
OL,17,FBrothers, took the row to the Supreme
OL,18,FCourt, telling a three-day hearing in
OL,19,FApril that the decision was an
OL,20,F"egregious error".
