OL,5,Crow
OL,7,FThe Financial Conduct Authority (FCA)
OL,8,Fhas also intervened in the case,
OL,9,Ftelling the UK's highest court that
OL,10,Fthe Court of Appeal ruling "goes too
OL,11,Ffar", while the three motorists oppose
OL,12,Fthe challenge.
OL,14,FLords Reed, Hodge, Lloyd-Jones, Briggs
OL,15,Fand Hamblen are due to hand down their
OL,16,Fruling at 4.35pm on Friday.
