OL,5,Crow
OL,7,FThe outcome of the ruling could have
OL,8,Fmajor consequences for the industry,
OL,9,Fwith the FCA telling the Supreme Court
OL,10,Flast year that almost 99% of the
OL,11,Froughly 32 million car finance
OL,12,Fagreements entered into since 2007
OL,13,Finvolved a commission payment to a
OL,14,Fbroker.
OL,16,FThe three drivers, Marcus Johnson,
OL,17,FAndrew Wrench and Amy Hopcraft, all
OL,18,Fused car dealers as brokers for
OL,19,Ffinance arrangements for second-hand
OL,20,Fcars, all worth less than #10,000.
