OL,5,Crow
OL,7,FOnly one finance option was presented
OL,8,Fto the motorists in each case, with
OL,9,Fthe car dealers making a profit from
OL,10,Fthe sale of the car and receiving
OL,11,Fcommission from the lender.
OL,13,FThe commission paid to dealers was
OL,14,Faffected by the interest rate on the
OL,15,Floan.
OL,17,FThe schemes were banned by the FCA in
OL,18,F2021, with the three drivers taking
OL,19,Flegal action individually between 2022
OL,20,Fand 2023.
