OL,5,Crow
OL,7,FIf justices dismiss the challenge, it
OL,8,Fis unclear how many people could be
OL,9,Fentitled to compensation.
OL,11,FIf they side with the lenders, then it
OL,12,Fis likely to significantly limit the
OL,13,Fscope of potential payouts to
OL,14,Fmotorists.
OL,16,FThe FCA has said it will confirm
OL,17,Fwithin six weeks of the judgment
OL,18,Fwhether it is planning to launch a
OL,19,Fredress scheme.
