OL,7,FWhat does the court case ruling mean
OL,8,Ffor you?
OL,10,FIf Supreme Court judges side with the
OL,11,Fclaimants then it could mean that many
OL,12,Fpeople who took out a car loan before
OL,13,F2021 may be due a payout, although it
OL,14,Fis difficult to say at this point how
OL,15,Fmany.
OL,17,FIf it sides with the lenders, then it
OL,18,Fis likely to significantly limit the
OL,19,Fscope of potential payouts to
OL,20,Fmotorists.
